---
description: Garantir que o arquivo api.py exponha apenas os endpoints e delegue toda a lógica para o cli.py.
globs:
  - api.py
  - cli.py
alwaysApply: true
rules:
  - Do not implement business or core logic directly in `api.py`.
  - All logic must be delegated to functions defined in `cli.py`.
  - API endpoints in `api.py` should act only as interfaces that call `cli.py` functions.
